"{\"uid\": \"themoderatevoice.com-2024-olympics-opening-what-the-hell-were-they-thinking\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Moderate Voice  An Internet hub with domestic and international news, analysis, original reporting, and popular features from the left, center, indies, centrists, moderates, and right  July 27, 2024byDavid RobertsonLeave a Comment    The opening ceremony of the 2024 Olympics has united people of all religious beliefs.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Atheists and Christians alike are condemning it.\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 337, \"end\": 347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.49272563340868564, \"rank\": 0.5219277249562984, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not just the religious symbolism in the opening ceremony that has people saying, \\\"What the hell were they thinking?\\\"\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The entire show appears to be the creation of someone who had a little too much LDS.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The kind of madness displayed in France rivals that of a Vulcan fraternity duringPon Farr.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.905782604841525, \"rank\": 0.05574100445434434, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 642, \"end\": 648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vulcan_Centaur\", \"score\": 0.9299280212359182, \"rank\": 0.07535204570710238, \"text\": \"Vulcan\", \"types\": [\"Q41291\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vulcan_Centaur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vulcan_Centaur\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sure, the people in charge of planning the ceremony were under pressure, but was it necessary for them to lose their heads over it?\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sure, the planners wanted to serve up something that would be unforgettable, but what they cooked up ended up putting a drag on their quest to please viewers.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This blogger would not object to a drag queen being in a satirical depiction of a painting that is historically inaccurate, but this live depiction is overkill.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then came the oversized Smurf who obviously ate somemagic mushrooms.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This blogger understood that the water events would be in Seine.\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1268, \"end\": 1273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999918599436817, \"rank\": 8.097808087511701e-06, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wasn't aware that the opening ceremony would be, too.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"Wanted\\\" posters say the following about David: \\\"Wanted: A refugee from planet Melmac masquerading as a human.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loves cats.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If seen, contact the Alien Task Force.\\\"\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Filed Under:Arts & Entertainment,Featured,France,InternationalTagged With:Olympics  Subscribe in a reader  Copyright 1998 - 2024 The Moderate Voice.Genesis Framework\\u00b7WordPress\\u00b7Log in\", \"from